A vast corporate building interior split dramatically down the middle in Studio Ghibli animation style: on the left side, rigid grey cubicles arranged in perfect military rows with identical workers at identical machines, everything monochrome and oppressive with harsh angular shadows; on the right side, the same space transforms into a lush, organic workspace where colorful floating platforms hold diverse workstations, gentle spirits drift between employees using varied devices, soft magical light streams through enormous windows, and small friendly creatures assist workers tinkering with glowing gadgets. In the center, a winding golden path bridges both worlds, with curious employees cautiously stepping from the grey zone toward the vibrant side, their clothes gradually gaining color as they cross. Whimsical clouds float through the open ceiling on the right, while mechanical gears and pipes dominate the left. The overall feeling captures transformation from control to creative freedom, rendered in soft watercolor textures with Miyazaki's signature warmth and wonder.
